# ResourceManagerSystem

## Purpose
One-shot initialization system. On the first frame, loads all textures, fonts, shaders, and UI
layouts from `Assets/Engine/ResourcesManifest.json` and `Assets/App/ResourcesManifest.json`, then
creates ResourceMapSingletonComponent containing the fully populated asset maps.
No-op on all subsequent frames (presence check guards early exit).

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | read | Presence-check only; if present, system exits immediately |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | add (deferred) | Created once; holds texture, shader, font, and UI layout maps keyed by UUID |
